MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2007-1829. Cesarespada v. Bandlow.

Cuyahoga App. No. 88835, 2007-0hio-4062. On appellants’ motion for compliance with Section 2(c), Article IV of the Ohio Constitution and appellee’s motion to strike appellants’ motion. Appellants’ motion denied. Appellee’s motion denied as moot.
